  "texts": [
    "Thus, we have encouraged students to use such generative models to potentially improve their productivity and efficiency.",
    "To analyze the usage of LLMs (i.e.",
    "ChatGPT, Copilot), we instructed students to annotate such generated code and document the prompts used.",
    "Section 2.2 explains the annotation and documentation process, along with how we used the data for analysis.",
    "In our study, unlike most undergraduate courses where the usage of LLMs is explicitly prohibited, we actively allowed students to employ LLMs if they believed these tools would enhance their productivity."
